# git column

> Display data in columns
> More information: https://git-scm.com/docs/git-column

- Format the stdin as multiple columns:

`ls | git column --mode={any something}`

- Format the stdin as multiple columns with a maximum width of `100`:

`ls | git column --mode=column --width={int number: 100}`

- Format the stdin as multiple columns with a maximum padding of `30`:

`ls | git column --mode=column --padding={int number: 30}`
